  "system": {
    "description": "<p>A mainstay of freebooting merchant-adventurers, the free merchant is an extremely versatile craft, hauling significant cargo to neighboring systems with very few hands. Its sandthrower discourages pirate shuttles and small craft; the multifocal laser lets a skilled gunner snipe important systems on an attacker, though the hull lacks the armor to stand up to a true warship.</p><p><strong>Crew:</strong> 1/6. <strong>Cargo:</strong> 160 tons. <strong>Cost:</strong> 775,000cr base price, 38,750cr six-month maintenance, 131,400cr yearly crew cost (3 crew).</p>",
